title: Dialogue 1
translated: But... there's nothing I can do...

title: Dialogue 2
translated: The mental images just start overflowing and my body just starts reacting on it's own.

title: Dialogue 3
translated: Surely Miss Hibiki saw you in that state

title: Dialogue 4
translated: and felt a sense of camaraderie.

title: Dialogue 5
translated:
Also if one were to mention Miss Hibiki's recent conversation topics...

They were all about you, Miss Nene.

title: Dialogue 6
translated: Maybe she's happy to be able to share her experiences.

title: Dialogue 9
translated: Oh dear, it seems my tongue has slipped.

title: Dialogue 10
translated:
Please treat that as off-the-record.

Otherwise I will be scolded by Miss Hibiki...
